entry.title: Turkey Lays Out Demands as Finland, Sweden Plan NATO Entry
entry.content: Stockholm said that senior officials from Sweden, Finland and Turkey will meet in Ankara to discuss the matter.

entry.title: Ukraine's Military Gains Raise Kyiv's War Aims
entry.content: Kharkiv’s regional governor said that even as Ukraine wins back territory seized by Russia in recent months, the situation across the region remains volatile.

entry.title: ​U.S., EU Boost Trade Ties to Fix Shortages, Counter Russia and China
entry.content: Senior U.S. and European Union officials agreed to expand cooperation on supply chains for critical technologies including semiconductors and materials used in their production.
